# PicoRAM Wipe On - 3x3 Merlin/Lights-Out style puzzle with OLED graphics and sound.
# Goal: turn all 9 cells ON. Press 1-9 to toggle the Merlin regions. 0 starts a new puzzle.
# Requires PicoRAM SOUND mode for 50D tones; no firmware changes. One bank, no nested CALL/RET.
